io.parallec.core

Class ResponseOnSingleTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.parallec.core.ResponseOnSingleTask

  • public class ResponseOnSingleTask
extends java.lang.Object
    this includes the request each target host will have one. isError() is true: means fail to receive response. Note that by default, the response content is not saved into the singleTaskResponse. Unless the user change the config by calling ParallelTaskBuilder.setSaveResponseToTask(boolean)
    Author:
    Yuanteng (Jeff) Pei
